snippet.title: Top 20 Pokemon That SHOULDN'T Exist

localized.description:
EDIT 9/27/14
OH MY GOD. I DON'T HATE POKEMON. I absolutely love the series and I always have since I was a kid. A lot of these pokemon are actually pretty good in the competitive game, but that's not what the list was based on. The list was solely based on the design/concept of these pokemon, and how ridiculous and uninspired they are.
- - - - - - - - - -
Which Pokemon are the worst of the worst? Gatorsdad, Jerranttheman, Vince (FreeThrowmpro/Vofafo) and I are here to find out!

Follow me on FaceBook! https://www.facebook.com/silokhawk

Special thanks to Ryan Reichert! http://www.ryanreichert.me

Apparently I used Spoink art from this lovely, my bad!  http://www.clinkorz.deviantart.com
